bjouhier,"As an application developer, you control how your code will be deployed; you can guarantee that operation xyz will only scan files that the application can always read and write. If not, it just means that something has compromised the deployment of the application (and you're likely to have a security issue). Same thing for race conditions.",FALSE,FALSE,57,36,92,4,FALSE,TRUE,FALSE,TRUE,0,37
